{
  "texts": [
    "Prompt LearningPrompt learning is an emerging technique which stimulates the capabilities of LLMs through designing proper prompts.Unlike traditional fine-tuning, where model parameters are directly updated, this approach emphasizes the crucial role of well-crafted prompts in guiding language models to produce more accurate and contextually relevant outputs.",
    "Moreover, by constructing effective prompts, LLMs can be customized for new tasks without costly training.",
    "This makes prompt learning much more practical and applicable in various natural language processing domains.",
    "In this work, we find that different prompts significantly impact the ability of LLMs to leverage external information and influence the performance of the generated outputs.",
    "By carefully designing prompts tailored for our RAG system, the generation quality of the LLM is greatly improved."
  ]
}